{"tid":884494,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中學最後一次陸運會","createTime":"2018-10-31T15:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T15:51:18.000Z","uid":196050,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"50be75a3fa918c5fd4c3dab320880b6053d26f9e","tid":884494,"uid":196050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:40:29.000Z","msg":"話說今年已經中六，今日係中學生涯裏面最後一次陸運會<br />\n自己本身冇乜運動細胞，但係就比人推左去跑班接，做歡樂組小丑<br />\n橫掂都係最後一次，不如做返一場令自己無憾嘅事<br />\n於是我喺接棒之後雙手擺係背後<br />\n學火影忍者跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑緊嗰陣仲隱約咁聽到啲form1仔喺到嗌<br />\n「火影呀，火影呀！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑完交完棒之後啲負責老師目定口呆<br />\n畢業班啲同學對我讚不絕口<br />\n跑最後一棒嘅班主任原本承認我一齊扮火影跑<br />\n但最後都喺怕柒甩底<br />\n<br />\n呢件事望落好似好青春，但其實諗返轉頭真喺好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32a35ffb42b6ac9840d82231cc82d91de54f2df","tid":884494,"uid":10325,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"-.-"},{"pid":"a7a1d3f96f142e19facbf268cd459affa9f63044","tid":884494,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:43:35.000Z","msg":"扮病走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bc4cfea03fa9e74e0982e1cb6b718853d9dbc4","tid":884494,"uid":205143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"雖然知係假但都幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda3085ad2368e22b04ee103262d9e1af5bd2b93","tid":884494,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食咗幾條女之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc9527060efb6caafdb41f32ad0900f95786af9","tid":884494,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"😂😂🤙🏻🤙🏻🤙🏻"}]}